Circles of radius 2 and X are externally tangent and are circumscribed by a third circle, as shown in the figure. Find the area of the shaded region. Express your answer in terms of $\pi$.

[asy]
fill(Circle((-1,0),5),gray(0.7));
fill(Circle((-3,0),3),white);
fill(circle((2,0),2),white);
